  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "windowing",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/windowing/yunxi/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.84,
      "size": 29376,
      "text": "要分析一段信号的频率，我们只能截取有限的一段来计算。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "windowing",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/windowing/yunxi/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.83,
      "size": 29232,
      "text": "可这一刀切下去，信号的两端被硬生生截断了。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "windowing",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/windowing/yunxi/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.67,
      "size": 26784,
      "text": "这个突兀的边缘，会给频谱带来意想不到的麻烦。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "windowing",
      "section_id": "leakage",
      "line_id": "leak-1",
      "filename": "leakage-leak-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/windowing/yunxi/leakage-leak-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.11,
      "size": 33696,
      "text": "本该是一根干净的谱线，却向两侧渗出许多小的杂散能量。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "windowing",
      "section_id": "leakage",
      "line_id": "leak-2",
      "filename": "leakage-leak-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/windowing/yunxi/leakage-leak-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.82,
      "size": 29088,
      "text": "这就是频谱泄漏，真实频率被涂抹到了周围一大片。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "windowing",
      "section_id": "leakage",
      "line_id": "leak-3",
      "filename": "leakage-leak-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/windowing/yunxi/leakage-leak-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.94,
      "size": 31104,
      "text": "罪魁祸首，正是矩形窗那两个陡峭的直角边缘。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "windowing",
      "section_id": "window",
      "line_id": "win-3",
      "filename": "window-win-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/windowing/yunxi/window-win-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.99,
      "size": 31824,
      "text": "边缘不再突兀，泄漏出去的杂散能量就大大减少了。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "windowing",
      "section_id": "tradeoff",
      "line_id": "trade-1",
      "filename": "tradeoff-trade-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/windowing/yunxi/tradeoff-trade-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.88,
      "size": 30096,
      "text": "频谱里高高的中间部分叫主瓣，两侧的小峰叫旁瓣。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "windowing",
      "section_id": "tradeoff",
      "line_id": "trade-3",
      "filename": "tradeoff-trade-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/windowing/yunxi/tradeoff-trade-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.26,
      "size": 36144,
      "text": "布莱克曼窗旁瓣压得最低，代价是主瓣变宽、分辨率下降。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "windowing",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/windowing/yunxi/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.05,
      "size": 32832,
      "text": "截断造成泄漏，加窗让边缘平滑，泄漏随之减小。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "windowing",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/windowing/yunxi/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.76,
      "size": 28224,
      "text": "窄主瓣与低旁瓣不可兼得，要按需求取舍。"
    }
  ],
  "total_duration": 21.15,
  "total_size": 338400
}